      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A4 Premium Plus that perfectly balances performance and luxury. This vehicle features a brilliant Mythos Black Metallic exterior that retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though it shows the honest character of regular use with minor stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the Nougat Brown leather interior remains supple and inviting; the seats show minimal wear on the bolsters, and the cabin is entirely free of any smoke or pet odors. Mechanically, this Audi is in robust health, having followed a strict factory service schedule with all records available. The turbocharged engine delivers smooth, responsive power, paired with a seamless transmission and the legendary Quattro all-wheel-drive system for confident handling. All technological features, including the intuitive Virtual Cockpit, navigation, and the premium Bang & Olufsen sound system, function flawlessly. The tires were recently replaced and offer excellent tread depth, while the brakes provide firm, consistent stopping power. This is a reliable, well-cared-for executive sedan that is ready for the road today.",
